{"tid":1294590,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"提防內鬼！將軍澳民生關注組係鬼，請廣傳！","createTime":"2019-07-07T20:23:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T17:50:40.000Z","uid":78336,"like":228,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"232afe80965ebb983a18f9e96bc9f51740e42705","tid":1294590,"uid":78336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T20:23:23.000Z","msg":"第一，<span style=\"color: red;\">遊行路線詭異，提防引君入甕</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1294564/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1294564/page/1</a><br />\n隔離有巴打已經講左 將軍澳地形有咩問題<br />\n<br />\n第二，<span style=\"color: red;\">HK01極速為此宣傳，極為可疑</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/30li8Id\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F30li8Id&d=Tc8prIKBo9hF1z3tnQ%2BJRoMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=c3687c0e\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/30li8Id</a><br />\n試問區政聯盟同將軍澳民生關注組有咩號召力可以令到紅媒01為其宣傳？<br />\n<br />\n第三，<span style=\"color: red;\">將軍澳民生關注組背景極不可靠</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Jk48ZO\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Jk48ZO&d=Tc8prIKBo9hF1z3tnQ%2BJRoMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=1d167be9\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Jk48ZO</a><br />\n其召集人陳展浚冒認學民思潮籌款。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180726/58487602\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180726%2F58487602&d=Tc8prIKBo9hF1z3tnQ%2BJRoMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=423364b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180726%2F58487602&h=3e5241b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180726/58487602</a><br />\n盜用楊岳橋名義宣傳<br />\n<br />\n光復將軍澳行動究竟值唔值得參加，諸君慎思。"},{"pid":"ba44d451d5fb1546ff61d1fbe6ac7d660618c24d","tid":1294590,"uid":78336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T20:24:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0a665d75dd1e3